Version 2.12:
- [!] 13 Sep 2007, Sheriff - Bug (0015925): The button "Add to cart" was changed to "Update" after sending an ecard. Fixed.
- [+] 5 Sep 2007, Alien - Improvement (0022000): The module is adapted to commercial design schemes.
- [+] 31 Jul 2007, Alien - Improvement (0015635): The gift certificate expiration date is added to ecards sent to recipient
- [!] 30 Jul 2007, Alien - Bug (0023738): When an order was edited in AOM, order total was calculated incorrectly, if the order was partially paid by GC. Fixed.
- [+] 26 Jul 2007, Alien - Improvement (0006793): Active gift certificates are now displayed on the customer's profile page.
- [+] 25 Jul 2007, Alien - Improvement (0014537): The ability to specify expiration date for gift certificates was added.
- [!] 13 Jun 2007, Alien - Bug (0021777): Some buttons were displayed incorrectly in the customer area. Fixed.

Version 2.11:
- [+] 12 Apr 2007, Sheriff - Improvement (0017395): The module templates were corrected to be W3C compatible.
- [+] 10 Apr 2007, Sheriff - Improvement (0018416): Refactoring of the PHP code was done to be compatible with some configurations of PHP 5.X.
- [!] 19 Jan 2007, Osipov - Bug (0015605): During the export of the customer zone templates, admin area templates were added to the list. Fixed.

Version 2.10:
- [!] 26 Sep 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0011232): The simultaneous operation of the AOM and GiftCertificates modules caused displaying an extra html header in the e-mailed order invoices. Fixed.

Version 2.9:
- [!] 21 Feb 2006, Osipov - Bug (0005946): After a product was added to the shopping cart, the cart total amount was calculated wrongly. The correct total amount value appeared only after the cart was updated. Fixed
- [!] 10 Feb 2006, Osipov - Bug (0005829): After an order's status had been changed from "Q" to "P" for the first time, links to downloadable files were not displayed correctly in the invoice e-mailed to the customer. Fixed.
- [!] 10 Feb 2006, Osipov - Bug (0005738): Wrong template definition in the class CEcardSelect. Fixed.
- [!] 20 Jan 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0005592): There was a problem with e-Cards not getting attached to gift certificates (when administrator created a GC and specified an e-Card to be attached to that GC, the email was sent without any attachments). Fixed.
- [!] 10 Jan 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0005500): In the process of gift certificate redemption, no checkup was performed to find out, whether the mandatory 'Gift Certificate' field contained an empty value. Fixed.

Version 2.8:
- [!] 25 Nov 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0005001): 'Gift certificates shipping cost' option didn't apply sometimes (when GC shipping cost was used and only online shipping methods were available). Fixed.
- [!] 15 Nov 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0004885): A few typos were fixed.
- [!] 07 Mar 2005, Asd - Bug: The compiled code/templates cache was not cleaned up during the module uninstallation. Fixed.

Version 2.7:
 - [!] 21 Feb 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The calculation of the tax on the GC was incorrect (when the "included VAT" option was enabled and the new improved VAT scheme calculation was implemented). Fixed.
 - [+] 17 Feb 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: An additional functionality was added to show GC details in the order details in the admin zone. Now the admin will be able to click on the "Payed by GC" link and see the GC details.

Version 2.6:
 - [!] 11 Jan 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The "debit" and "status" values were incorrect (if a customer payed by a GC). These values did not change when an order was processed. Fixed.

Version 2.5:
 - [!] 13 Dec 2004, Sheriff - Bug: The "shipping cost" value in the customer cart "total" section was incorrect (if a customer added a GC with the "Send via Postal Mail" option). The common shipping cost was displayed instead of the calculated shipping cost of the GC. Fixed. 

